        public static AnonymizerStatus decompress(java.io.File inFile,
                          java.io.File outFile)
        Convert the transfer syntax of the input file to EVRLE, writing the result to the output file. The input and output files are allowed to be the same.
        Parameters:
        inFile - the file to anonymize.
        outFile - the output file, which may be same as inFile you if want to decompress in place.
        Returns:
        the static status result
